parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling and restarting issues can cause the vehicle to lose power and control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine stalls and shuts off while driving

requiring the vehicle to be put in park and restarted; the vehicle stalls and shuts off while slowing down or coming to a stop; the vehicle stalls and shuts off randomly; the start/stop system malfunctions; the electronics glitch and shut off; the vehicle requires manual restart.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: False Collision Warnings and Emergency Braking
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The false collision warnings and emergency braking can cause the vehicle to suddenly stop or slow down, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The forward collision warning activates out of the blue; the automatic emergency braking is applied for no reason; the vehicle suddenly stops or slows down; the vehicle seizes up and comes to a screeching halt.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The door and window malfunctions can cause the vehicle to be unsafe to drive, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The windows roll down or up randomly; the doors do not lock or unlock; the parking brake engages while driving; the driver side window does not open manually; the rear window rolls down part way.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical and sensor issues can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The LED daytime running lights go out; the headlights go out; the door wiring harness fails; the passenger airbag light comes on and off; the vehicle's electronics malfunction; the start/stop system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the deployment of airbags without a crash, or the failure to deploy airbags in the event of a crash, which can cause injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag deploys unexpectedly
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the passenger airbag is not recognized
the airbag system error message is displayed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake noise and grinding issues can cause a loss of confidence in the vehicle's braking system, potentially leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Loud grinding
metal-on-metal noise when braking
vibrations or pulsation in the pedal or steering wheel
squealing and grinding noises when applying the brake
deep grinding sound every 4
000 miles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended brake engagement can cause sudden stops, potentially leading to accidents or near-misses, and can also cause a loss of control of the vehicle.
symptoms: Unintended engagement of the emergency brake
sudden stops
loud warning lights
and sudden application of the parking brake while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake system failure can cause a loss of braking ability, potentially leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: Failure of the brake system
inability to stop the vehicle
rolling through stop signs
and loss of braking ability.
